essing your grass\n5:57 - Hairstyle reference picture\n8:00- Asking you some questions\n10:22 - Offering you treats and tea\n13:02 - Bedazzled sweets\n14:14 - Pouring your tea, sugars\n16:04 - Bag rummaging\n16:57 - Applying detangler/heat protectant\n17:53 - Bedazzled Comb, camera touching\n18:37 - Combing your grass\n22:24 - Bedazzled straightening iron\n25:11 - Spring scrunchies\n27:58 - Bedazzled scissors\n29:14 - Trimming the ends\n30:57 - Grass brushing, camera touching\n32:00 - Trimming again\n33:51 - Bang length check\n34:49 - Sectioning your grass\n37:17 - Snipping your bangs\n39:16 - Brushing forward\n39:57 - Adding more layers\n41:23 - Wetting and scrunching it\n42:49 - Button Blowdryer\n45:04 - Styling bangs with curling iron\n48:50 - Bedazzled mirror, see your look\n50:38 - Choose your flowers\n51:54 - Plucking leaves from your roots\n52:49 - Braiding your hair\n56:05 - Smooth with pomade\n58:00 - Cutting flowers, adding to braids\n1:02:33 - Whispered Outro\n\n__\n\nThanks for watching!!\nmuch love,\nJocie\n\nHi! My name is Jocie (they/she), and I'm just a human happy to be creating ASMR videos : )\n\nI post what I enjoy, meaning lots of:\n\nMAKEUP \u0026 SKINCARE\nPERSONAL ATTENTION\nFANTASY ROLEPLAYS\n\u0026 NATURE\n\nNew videos TUESDAYS 6PM EST and/or whenever else I can post!\n\nFor someone practicing to slow down \u0026 be kind to themselves, I find ASMR gives us a chance for pause, encouraging us to take time for self care and to prioritize our wellbeing. I hope we can all use this channel to practice love, laugh a little, and relax ♡ SUBSCRIBE and join in on the tingles!\n\n*Shopping from the tagged products helps me receive a small commission from your purchase. Know that there's no pressure whatsoever to buy anything. Thank you for the support : )\n#asmr","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":707,"length":37,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAciEwjwiLCQs56UAxXvRvIAHVKXGdyaAQMIsQHKAQT95OY0","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadat